debugQuery.query: SELECT DATE_FORMAT(PM_LTE_ALGO_CELL.DATE, '%Y-%m') AS COL_1,CM_AUDIT_INFO_SITES_2.REGION AS COL_2,ROUND(((0.1*(EXP(IFNULL(((SUM(IFNULL(PM_ERAB_REL_CELL.L_ERAB_ABNORMREL_QCI_5,0)+IFNULL(PM_ERAB_REL_CELL.L_ERAB_ABNORMREL_MME_QCI_5,0))/SUM(IFNULL(PM_ERAB_REL_CELL.L_ERAB_NORMREL_QCI_5,0)+IFNULL(PM_ERAB_REL_CELL.L_ERAB_ABNORMREL_QCI_5,0)+IFNULL(PM_ERAB_REL_CELL.L_ERAB_NORMREL_IRATHOOUT_QCI_5,0)+IFNULL(PM_ERAB_REL_CELL.L_ERAB_ABNORMREL_MME_QCI_5,0))))*100*(-50),0))))+(0.3*(EXP(IFNULL((SUM(IFNULL(PM_HO_IRAT_OUT_CELL.L_IRATHO_SRVCC_E2W_EXECSUCCOUT,0))+SUM(IFNULL(PM_HO_IRAT_OUT_CELL.L_IRATHO_SRVCC_E2G_EXECSUCCOUT,0)))/(SUM(IFNULL(PM_ERAB_REL_CELL.L_ERAB_NORMREL_QCI_1,0))+SUM(IFNULL(PM_ERAB_REL_CELL.L_ERAB_ABNORMREL_QCI_1,0))+SUM(IFNULL(PM_ERAB_REL_CELL.L_ERAB_NORMREL_IRATHOOUT_QCI_1,0))+SUM(IFNULL(PM_ERAB_REL_CELL.L_ERAB_ABNORMREL_MME_VOIP,0)))*100*(-8.83344),0))))+(0.3*(EXP(IFNULL((SUM(IFNULL(PM_ERAB_REL_CELL.L_ERAB_ABNORMREL_QCI_1,0)+IFNULL(PM_ERAB_REL_CELL.L_ERAB_ABNORMREL_MME_VOIP,0))/SUM(IFNULL(PM_ERAB_REL_CELL.L_ERAB_NORMREL_QCI_1,0)+IFNULL(PM_ERAB_REL_CELL.L_ERAB_ABNORMREL_QCI_1,0)+IFNULL(PM_ERAB_REL_CELL.L_ERAB_NORMREL_IRATHOOUT_QCI_1,0)+IFNULL(PM_ERAB_REL_CELL.L_ERAB_ABNORMREL_MME_VOIP,0)))*100*(-50),0))))+(0.3*EXP((1-IFNULL(((SUM(IFNULL(PM_LTE_RRC_SETUP_CELL.L_RRC_CONNREQ_SUCC,0))*SUM(IFNULL(PM_ERAB_EST_CELL.L_S1SIG_CONNEST_SUCC,0))*SUM(IFNULL(PM_ERAB_EST_CELL.L_ERAB_SUCCEST_QCI_5,0))*SUM(IFNULL(PM_ERAB_EST_CELL.L_ERAB_SUCCEST_QCI_1,0)-IFNULL(PM_ERAB_EST_CELL.L_ERAB_INITSUCCEST_QCI_1,0))))/(SUM(IFNULL(PM_LTE_RRC_SETUP_CELL.L_RRC_CONNREQ_ATT,0))*SUM(IFNULL(PM_ERAB_EST_CELL.L_S1SIG_CONNEST_ATT,0))*SUM(IFNULL(PM_ERAB_EST_CELL.L_ERAB_ATTEST_QCI_5,0))*(SUM(IFNULL(PM_ERAB_EST_CELL.L_ERAB_ATTEST_QCI_1,0))-SUM(IFNULL(PM_ERAB_EST_CELL.L_ERAB_INITATTEST_QCI_1,0))-SUM(IFNULL(PM_ERAB_ESTFAIL_CELL.L_ERAB_FAILEST_X2AP_VOIP,0)))),1))*(-65))))*100,2) AS COL_3,ROUND(IFNULL(100*((IFNULL(SUM(IFNULL(PM_LTE_RRC_SETUP_CELL.L_RRC_CONNREQ_SUCC,0))/SUM(IFNULL(PM_LTE_RRC_SETUP_CELL.L_RRC_CONNREQ_ATT,0)),1)*IFNULL(SUM(IFNULL(PM_ERAB_EST_CELL.L_S1SIG_CONNEST_SUCC,0))/SUM(IFNULL(PM_ERAB_EST_CELL.L_S1SIG_CONNEST_ATT,0)),1)*IFNULL(SUM(IFNULL(PM_ERAB_EST_CELL.L_ERAB_SUCCEST_QCI_5,0))/SUM(IFNULL(PM_ERAB_EST_CELL.L_ERAB_ATTEST_QCI_5,0)),1)*IFNULL((SUM(IFNULL(PM_ERAB_EST_CELL.L_ERAB_SUCCEST_QCI_1,0))-SUM(IFNULL(PM_ERAB_EST_CELL.L_ERAB_INITSUCCEST_QCI_1,0)))/(SUM(IFNULL(PM_ERAB_EST_CELL.L_ERAB_ATTEST_QCI_1,0))-SUM(IFNULL(PM_ERAB_EST_CELL.L_ERAB_INITATTEST_QCI_1,0))-SUM(IFNULL(PM_ERAB_ESTFAIL_CELL.L_ERAB_FAILEST_X2AP_VOIP,0))),1))),0),2) AS COL_4,ROUND(IFNULL(100*(SUM(IFNULL(PM_ERAB_REL_CELL.L_ERAB_ABNORMREL_QCI_1,0)+IFNULL(PM_ERAB_REL_CELL.L_ERAB_ABNORMREL_MME_VOIP,0)))/(SUM(IFNULL(PM_ERAB_REL_CELL.L_ERAB_NORMREL_QCI_1,0)+IFNULL(PM_ERAB_REL_CELL.L_ERAB_ABNORMREL_QCI_1,0)+IFNULL(PM_ERAB_REL_CELL.L_ERAB_ABNORMREL_MME_VOIP,0)+IFNULL(PM_ERAB_REL_CELL.L_ERAB_NORMREL_IRATHOOUT_QCI_1,0))),0),2) AS COL_5,ROUND(IFNULL(100*(SUM(IFNULL(PM_ERAB_REL_CELL.L_ERAB_ABNORMREL_QCI_5,0)+IFNULL(PM_ERAB_REL_CELL.L_ERAB_ABNORMREL_MME_QCI_5,0)))/(SUM(IFNULL(PM_ERAB_REL_CELL.L_ERAB_NORMREL_QCI_5,0)+IFNULL(PM_ERAB_REL_CELL.L_ERAB_ABNORMREL_MME_QCI_5,0)+IFNULL(PM_ERAB_REL_CELL.L_ERAB_ABNORMREL_QCI_5,0)+IFNULL(PM_ERAB_REL_CELL.L_ERAB_NORMREL_IRATHOOUT_QCI_5,0))),0),2) AS COL_6,ROUND(IFNULL(100*SUM(IFNULL(PM_ERAB_REL_CELL.L_ERAB_ABNORMREL_QCI_1,0)+IFNULL(PM_ERAB_REL_CELL.L_ERAB_ABNORMREL_QCI_5,0)+IFNULL(PM_ERAB_REL_CELL.L_ERAB_ABNORMREL_MME_QCI_5,0)+IFNULL(PM_ERAB_REL_CELL.L_ERAB_ABNORMREL_MME_VOIP,0))/SUM(IFNULL(PM_ERAB_REL_CELL.L_ERAB_NORMREL_QCI_1,0)+IFNULL(PM_ERAB_REL_CELL.L_ERAB_ABNORMREL_QCI_1,0)+IFNULL(PM_ERAB_REL_CELL.L_ERAB_ABNORMREL_MME_QCI_5,0)+IFNULL(PM_ERAB_REL_CELL.L_ERAB_NORMREL_QCI_5,0)+IFNULL(PM_ERAB_REL_CELL.L_ERAB_ABNORMREL_MME_VOIP,0)+IFNULL(PM_ERAB_REL_CELL.L_ERAB_NORMREL_IRATHOOUT_QCI_1,0)+IFNULL(PM_ERAB_REL_CELL.L_ERAB_NORMREL_IRATHOOUT_QCI_5,0)+IFNULL(PM_ERAB_REL_CELL.L_ERAB_ABNORMREL_QCI_5,0)),0),2) AS COL_7,ROUND(IFNULL((SUM(IFNULL(PM_HO_IRAT_OUT_CELL.L_IRATHO_SRVCC_E2W_EXECSUCCOUT,0))+SUM(IFNULL(PM_HO_IRAT_OUT_CELL.L_IRATHO_SRVCC_E2G_EXECSUCCOUT,0)))/(SUM(IFNULL(PM_ERAB_REL_CELL.L_ERAB_NORMREL_QCI_1,0))+SUM(IFNULL(PM_ERAB_REL_CELL.L_ERAB_ABNORMREL_QCI_1,0))+SUM(IFNULL(PM_ERAB_REL_CELL.L_ERAB_NORMREL_IRATHOOUT_QCI_1,0))+SUM(IFNULL(PM_ERAB_REL_CELL.L_ERAB_ABNORMREL_MME_VOIP,0)))*100,0),2) AS COL_8,ROUND(SUM(PM_TRAFFIC_THRUPUT_CELL.L_ERAB_SESSIONTIME_HIGHPRECISION_QCI1)/(36000),4) AS COL_9,ROUND(IFNULL(((5*SUM(PM_LTE_ALGO_CELL.L_VOICE_E2EVQI_EXCELLENT_TIMES)+4*SUM(PM_LTE_ALGO_CELL.L_VOICE_E2EVQI_GOOD_TIMES)+3*SUM(PM_LTE_ALGO_CELL.L_VOICE_E2EVQI_ACCEPT_TIMES)+2*SUM(PM_LTE_ALGO_CELL.L_VOICE_E2EVQI_POOR_TIMES)+SUM(PM_LTE_ALGO_CELL.L_VOICE_E2EVQI_BAD_TIMES))/(SUM(PM_LTE_ALGO_CELL.L_VOICE_E2EVQI_EXCELLENT_TIMES)+SUM(PM_LTE_ALGO_CELL.L_VOICE_E2EVQI_GOOD_TIMES)+SUM(PM_LTE_ALGO_CELL.L_VOICE_E2EVQI_ACCEPT_TIMES)+SUM(PM_LTE_ALGO_CELL.L_VOICE_E2EVQI_POOR_TIMES)+SUM(PM_LTE_ALGO_CELL.L_VOICE_E2EVQI_BAD_TIMES))),0),4) AS COL_10 FROM PM_LTE_ALGO_CELL INNER JOIN PM_ERAB_REL_CELL ON PM_LTE_ALGO_CELL.DATE = PM_ERAB_REL_CELL.DATE AND PM_LTE_ALGO_CELL.SUBNETWORK = PM_ERAB_REL_CELL.SUBNETWORK AND PM_LTE_ALGO_CELL.ENODEB_FUNCTION_NAME = PM_ERAB_REL_CELL.ENODEB_FUNCTION_NAME AND PM_LTE_ALGO_CELL.CELL_NAME = PM_ERAB_REL_CELL.CELL_NAME INNER JOIN PM_HO_IRAT_OUT_CELL ON PM_LTE_ALGO_CELL.DATE = PM_HO_IRAT_OUT_CELL.DATE AND PM_LTE_ALGO_CELL.SUBNETWORK = PM_HO_IRAT_OUT_CELL.SUBNETWORK AND PM_LTE_ALGO_CELL.ENODEB_FUNCTION_NAME = PM_HO_IRAT_OUT_CELL.ENODEB_FUNCTION_NAME AND PM_LTE_ALGO_CELL.CELL_NAME = PM_HO_IRAT_OUT_CELL.CELL_NAME INNER JOIN PM_TRAFFIC_THRUPUT_CELL ON PM_LTE_ALGO_CELL.DATE = PM_TRAFFIC_THRUPUT_CELL.DATE AND PM_LTE_ALGO_CELL.SUBNETWORK = PM_TRAFFIC_THRUPUT_CELL.SUBNETWORK AND PM_LTE_ALGO_CELL.ENODEB_FUNCTION_NAME = PM_TRAFFIC_THRUPUT_CELL.ENODEB_FUNCTION_NAME AND PM_LTE_ALGO_CELL.CELL_NAME = PM_TRAFFIC_THRUPUT_CELL.CELL_NAME INNER JOIN PM_LTE_RRC_SETUP_CELL ON PM_LTE_ALGO_CELL.DATE = PM_LTE_RRC_SETUP_CELL.DATE AND PM_LTE_ALGO_CELL.SUBNETWORK = PM_LTE_RRC_SETUP_CELL.SUBNETWORK AND PM_LTE_ALGO_CELL.ENODEB_FUNCTION_NAME = PM_LTE_RRC_SETUP_CELL.ENODEB_FUNCTION_NAME AND PM_LTE_ALGO_CELL.CELL_NAME = PM_LTE_RRC_SETUP_CELL.CELL_NAME INNER JOIN PM_ERAB_EST_CELL ON PM_LTE_ALGO_CELL.DATE = PM_ERAB_EST_CELL.DATE AND PM_LTE_ALGO_CELL.SUBNETWORK = PM_ERAB_EST_CELL.SUBNETWORK AND PM_LTE_ALGO_CELL.ENODEB_FUNCTION_NAME = PM_ERAB_EST_CELL.ENODEB_FUNCTION_NAME AND PM_LTE_ALGO_CELL.CELL_NAME = PM_ERAB_EST_CELL.CELL_NAME INNER JOIN PM_ERAB_ESTFAIL_CELL ON PM_LTE_ALGO_CELL.DATE = PM_ERAB_ESTFAIL_CELL.DATE AND PM_LTE_ALGO_CELL.SUBNETWORK = PM_ERAB_ESTFAIL_CELL.SUBNETWORK AND PM_LTE_ALGO_CELL.ENODEB_FUNCTION_NAME = PM_ERAB_ESTFAIL_CELL.ENODEB_FUNCTION_NAME AND PM_LTE_ALGO_CELL.CELL_NAME = PM_ERAB_ESTFAIL_CELL.CELL_NAME LEFT JOIN CM_AUDIT_INFO_SITES_2 ON PM_LTE_ALGO_CELL.ENODEB_FUNCTION_NAME = CM_AUDIT_INFO_SITES_2.managed_object2 WHERE 1=1  AND  (PM_LTE_ALGO_CELL.DATE >= '2019-03-01' AND PM_LTE_ALGO_CELL.DATE <= '2019-03-31')  GROUP BY 1, 2 ORDER BY 2 ASC ,1 ASC
